Description: POCSAG paging protocol encoder/decoder library
 libpocsag is a C library for encoding and decoding POCSAG (Post Office
 Code Standardisation Advisory Group) paging protocol messages. It provides
 a batch encoder, streaming decoder, BCH(31,21) error correction, and
 support for numeric, alphanumeric, and tone-only message types.
